Let’s expand the product $(x+1)^2 \cdot x$.
\begin{align*}
(x+1)^2 \cdot x&=(x^2+2x+1)\cdot x\\
&=x^3+2x^2+x\\
&=\boxed{x^3+2x^2+x}
\end{align*}
